<levels>
	<level xmlPath="../Resources/Data/level0.xml" title="Out of the Blue" previewpicture="../Resources/Gfx/LevelSelect/actOne.dds">
A strange scent carries on the
breeze -- the stink of smoke.
Take wing and investigate.
<button normalsprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission00off.dds" hoversprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission00hover.dds" activesprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission00on.dds"/>
	</level>
	
	<level xmlPath="../Resources/Data/level1.xml" title="Reed before the Wind" previewpicture="../Resources/Gfx/LevelSelect/actOne.dds">
This foe is of brass and fire.
But the west wind is at your back,
and they will fall before us.
<button normalsprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission01off.dds" hoversprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission01hover.dds" activesprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission01on.dds"/>
	</level>
	
	<level xmlPath="../Resources/Data/level2.xml" title="Fire with Fire" previewpicture="../Resources/Gfx/LevelSelect/actOne.dds">
Their ships are corroded from smog.
Pierce the Foe&apos;s soot-black hulls,
and stab at their hearts.
<button normalsprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission02off.dds" hoversprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission02hover.dds" activesprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission02on.dds"/>
	</level>
	
	<level xmlPath="../Resources/Data/level3.xml" title="Weather the Storm" previewpicture="../Resources/Gfx/LevelSelect/actOne.dds">
Suicidal Foe pilots mean to
drag you down to the grave.
Survive their onslaught.
<button normalsprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission03off.dds" hoversprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission03hover.dds" activesprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission03on.dds"/>
	</level>
	
	<level xmlPath="../Resources/Data/level4.xml" title="Zone of Danger" previewpicture="../Resources/Gfx/LevelSelect/actOne.dds">
They choke the skies with
smoke and gunpowder.
Rip out their hearts.
<button normalsprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission04off.dds" hoversprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission04hover.dds" activesprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission04on.dds"/>
	</level>
	
	<level xmlPath="../Resources/Data/level5.xml" title="An ill Wind" previewpicture="../Resources/Gfx/LevelSelect/actTwo.dds">
The very air carries a greenish
tint, yet they cling to it madly.
Tear down their defenses.
<button normalsprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission05off.dds" hoversprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission05hover.dds" activesprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission05on.dds"/>
	</level>
	
	<level xmlPath="../Resources/Data/level6.xml" title="Skyfall" previewpicture="../Resources/Gfx/LevelSelect/actTwo.dds">
Not even the edge of the sky
seems a limit to their greed.
Their satellites must fall.
<button normalsprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission06off.dds" hoversprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission06hover.dds" activesprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission06on.dds"/>
	</level>
	
	<level xmlPath="../Resources/Data/level7.xml" title="Leviathan" previewpicture="../Resources/Gfx/LevelSelect/actTwo.dds">
The Foe has set in motion the
full might of their military machine.
Slay this monstrosity.
<button normalsprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission07off.dds" hoversprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission07hover.dds" activesprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission07on.dds"/>
	</level>
	
	<level xmlPath="../Resources/Data/level8.xml" title="Skies on Fire" previewpicture="../Resources/Gfx/LevelSelect/actThree.dds">
Missiles fill the smog-ridden sky
like gnats.
Destroy their droning hosts.
<button normalsprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission08off.dds" hoversprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission08hover.dds" activesprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission08on.dds"/>
	</level>
	
	<level xmlPath="../Resources/Data/level9.xml" title="The Sun in Chains" previewpicture="../Resources/Gfx/LevelSelect/actThree.dds">
Foe pilots swarm like piranha.
They must be growing desperate.
Break through.
<button normalsprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission09off.dds" hoversprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission09hover.dds" activesprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission09on.dds"/>
	</level>
	
	<level xmlPath="../Resources/Data/level10.xml" title="Mighty Oaks do Fall" previewpicture="../Resources/Gfx/LevelSelect/actThree.dds">
That dark mass on the horizon...
That&apos;s no moon.
<button normalsprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission10off.dds" hoversprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission10hover.dds" activesprite="../Resources\Gfx\Icons\missions/mission10on.dds"/>
	</level>
</levels>